"  BREAD CRUMBS AND SAUCE","1 1/2 cups fresh ciabatta bread crumbs*","1 1/2 tablespoons olive oil","1 1/8 teaspoons kosher salt, divided","  About 3/4 tsp. pepper, divided","3/4 teaspoon smoked sweet paprika","1/4 cup salted butter","1/4 cup flour","2 cups milk","2 cups shredded sharp cheddar cheese","  PASTA","12 ounces Barilla Pronto elbow macaroni (a one-pan, no-drain pasta)* or regular macaroni"